data.description: What more can you ask for than a 2000+ heated sqft home on over two acres? How about a large living room, a great kitchen and a really huge family room? Storage space you ask? There are two sheds in the backyard, one is 320 sqft and is all set for power to be run to it. All this in a quiet place in the country!!
